{
  "name": "CustomViews",
  "summary": "<p>每个视图由一个 <strong>CustomView</strong> 对象代表。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>CustomViews</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>CustomViews</strong> 集合。使用 <strong>Add</strong> 方法可新建自定义视图，并将它添加到 <strong>CustomViews</strong> 集合中。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在活动工作簿中新建一个自定义视图，并命名为“Summary”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Summary&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作簿上第一个自定义视图的名称为“example”，则展示该自定义视图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (customView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>) {\n        customView.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Show</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>由自定义工作簿视图组成的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作簿上自定义视图的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`自定义视图的数量：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${customViews.Count}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>新建自定义视图。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在活动工作簿中新建一个自定义视图，并命名为“Summary”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Summary&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作簿上新建一个自定义视图，并显示该工作簿上自定义视图的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>\n    customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example3&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customViews.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "ViewName",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "<p>新视图的名称。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "PrintSettings",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果为 True，则在自定义视图中包括打印设置。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "RowColSettings",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果为 True，则在自定义视图中包括隐藏行和隐藏列（包括筛选信息）的设置。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个 CustomView 对象，它代表新的自定义视图。</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示名为“example”的自定义视图中是否包含打印设置。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;example&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintSettings</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上所有自定义视图的名称赋值给活动工作表的单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customViews = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomViews</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= customViews.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = customViews.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "ViewName",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的名称或索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>包含在集合中的一个 CustomView 对象。</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}